<paragraph id="C13DE303055403D5AE6D609DAEF3C0A5" pageId="0" pageNumber="145">*China (Sichuan, Yunnan); Japan (Hokkaido, Honshu, Shikoku, Kyushu, Okinawa-Honto).</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
